  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcc\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 : \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bc7 \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bc1 : \u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 : \u0b89\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0baf \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9c\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "No Buddhist constructions on Kurundur Hill : Reconstruction is going on : Archeology Department informs court : Judges visit Kurundur Hill to find out the truth",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Deputy Solicitor General of the Attorney General's Department said that no new Buddhist constructions have been constructed on Kurundur hill, instead, actions are being taken to protect ancient symbols under the Act of the Department of Archaeology.",
        "The Mullaitivu Magistrate's Court had already on the 14th issued an order to the police to remove the new Buddhist constructions erected in Kurundurmalai and to submit a report to the court after removing them and to protect the archeological symbols properly.",
        "In this situation, the Mullaitivu Police filed a motion in the Mullaitivu Magistrate's Court stating that there is a problem in implementing the order given by the court and if it is implemented, there is a possibility of confusion between the races. Others were present in the forum.",
        "The Deputy Solicitor General was present on behalf of the Department of Archeology in today's hearing in the presence of Hon'ble Judge R. Saravanaraja. On behalf of the Ayyanar temple administration, senior lawyer Anton Phunitanayagam and lawyers from the Mullaitivu District Lawyers Association were present.",
        "During this, Deputy Solicitor General argued that Kurundurmalai is a Buddhist archaeological site and no new constructions are taking place there, instead, the process of maintaining and protecting archaeological symbols is being carried out under the archaeological laws. He told the court that the lawyers appearing on behalf of the Ayyanar temple have misled the court and obtained this verdict and another case has been filed in the Supreme Court regarding this temple issue and the lawyers who argued on behalf of the Ayyanar temple administration have not brought this case to the attention of the court.",
        "Lawyers including senior lawyer Anran Punitanayakam, who argued on behalf of Ayyanar Temple, pointed out in the court that the new constructions being erected in Kurundur Hill are new constructions under the guise of protecting archeological monuments. In accordance with the request of the Hon'ble Council and the Attorney General's Department officials to visit the construction in person, the Judge and the Attorney General's Department officers have now made a field visit to Kurundur Hill where the construction is taking place.-"
      ],
